0electric%20will%20be%20virtually%20100%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Clifford%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20talking%20200%20miles%2C%20it%20might%20only%20be%2050%25.%20Over%20that%2C%20it'd%20be%20zero%20at%20the%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20main%20issue%20was%20the%20limited%20energy%20density%20of%20batteries%2C%20which%20still%20don't%20offer%20the%20same%20storage%20capacity%20per%20weight%20and%20volume%20as%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Incat%20is%20focusing%20on%20ferries%20for%20high-density%2C%20relatively%20short%20routes%20like%20those%20in%20the%20English%20Channel%20or%20the%20Baltic%20Sea%20instead%20of%20oceangoing%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20ferry%20boat%20builders%2C%26quot%3B%20Clifford%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20a%20very%20large%20ferry%20for%20most%20routes%20would%20not%20go%20over%20about%20160%20meters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Incat's%20Hull%20096%20at%20a%20port.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6819ee9fc6ad288d14801d23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222136%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFerry%20operator%20Buquebus%20commissioned%20Incat%20to%20build%20a%20vessel%20to%20run%20between%20Buenos%20Aires%20and%20Uruguay.%3Cp%3EIncat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Clifford%20believes%20Hull%20096%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20clean%20maritime%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ship%20changes%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20earlier%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20building%20world-leading%20vessels%20here%20in%20Tasmania%20for%20more%20than%20four%20decades%2C%20and%20Hull%20096%20is%20the%20most%20ambitious%2C%20most%20complex%2C%20and%20most%20important%20project%20we've%20ever%20delivered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ferry%20boasts%20a%2040%20megawatt-hour