0a%20solo%20retreat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20booked%20a%20trip%20alone%20to%20Bali%20from%20D.C.%20and%20went%20with%20no%20itinerary%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20intention%20to%20enjoy%20myself%2C%20enjoy%20the%20sights%2C%20and%20look%20inward%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20I%20truly%20wanted%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trip%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20on%20a%20Black%20woman's%20version%20of%20Eat%2C%20Pray%2C%20Love.%20I%20turned%20off%20my%20phone%20and%20computer%2C%20connected%20with%20strangers%2C%20and%20did%20things%20like%20breath%20work%20and%20meditation%2C%20just%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20mind%20and%20thoughts%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20practices%20helped%20quiet%20the%20noise%20and%20fear%20of%20being%20laid%20off.%20It%20shifted%20the%20way%20I%20viewed%20myself%2C%20and%20the%20possibilities%20I%20could%20see%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20like%20I%20became%20the%20main%20character%20of%20my%20own%20life.%20Before%20the%20layoff%2C%20I%20would%20often%20ask%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20I%20do%20to%20make%20this%20organization%20better%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20now%20I%20began%20to%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20my%20goals%2C%20my%20strengths%3F%20What%20would%20I%20love%20to%20be%20doing%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis%3F%20If%20I'm%20not%20reacting%20out%20of%20hurt%2C%20embarrassment%2C%20or%20the%20need%20to%20prove%20I'm%20good%20enough%20to%20land%20another%20job%20right%20away%2C%20what%20do%20I%20truly%20want%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20me%2C%20the%20answer%20was%20founding%20my%20company%2C%20Power%20Coaching%20and%20Consulting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226a8b997-99d0-46ba-9ce8-03451623f8ea%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20now%20a%20coach%2C%20and%20I%20plan%20to%20run%20retreats%20in%20the%20next%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%2