and%20pouring%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20into%20a%20degree%20doesn't%20always%20yield%20the%20same%20results%2C%20he%20says%2C%20as%20he%20hears%20about%20people%20taking%20on%20lots%20of%20debt%20and%20then%20struggling%20to%20find%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20eyeing%20the%20ever-rising%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Faverage-college-tuition%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520average%2520college%2520tuition%2520for%2Cincreased%25203.2%2525%2520year%2520over%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecost%20of%20college%20tuition%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20roiling%20uncertainty%20in%20many%20white-collar%20career%20fields%2C%20and%20are%20choosing%20an%20alternate%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20are%20losing%20faith%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-college-university-war-get-rich-quick-schemes-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EROI%20of%20a%20college%20degree%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%202023%20Gallup%20poll%2C%20only%2036%25%20of%20respondents%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20deal%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bquite%20a%20lot%26quot%3B%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20higher%20education%20system%2C%20dropping%20from%2057%25%20in%202015.%20A%20Pew%20Research%20study%20in%202024%20found%20that%20just%2022%25%20of%20US%20adults%20thought%20that%20college%20was%20worth%20it%20if%20a%20student%20had%20to%20take%20out%20loans%20to%20attend.%20Zoomers%20are%20also%20most%20likely%20to%20feel%20that%20getting%20a%20degree%20is%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20and%20money%2C%20a%202025%20survey%20from%20Indeed%20found.%20Per%20Experian%2C%20the%20average%20Gen%20Zer%20has%20about%20%2423%2C000%20in%20student%20debt.%20That%20load%20is%20starting%20to%20feel%20heavier%20now%20that%20the%20perks%20Gen%20Zers%20most%20want%20%E2%80%94%20including%20work-life%20balance%2C%20financial%20stability%2C%20and%20a%20p