to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20close%20your%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20cofounder%20of%20VC%20firm%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20tech%20show%20TBPN%20published%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BImagine%20two%20states%20of%20the%20world%3A%20One%20in%20which%20the%20entire%20world%20runs%20on%20American%20open-source%20LLM%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20where%20the%20entire%20world%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20runs%20on%20all%20Chinese%20software.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreessen's%20comments%20come%20amid%20an%20intensifying%20US-China%20tech%20rivalry%20and%20a%20growing%20debate%20over%20open-%20and%20closed-source%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpen-source%20models%20are%20freely%20accessible%2C%20allowing%20anyone%20to%20study%2C%20modify%2C%20and%20build%20upon%20them.%20Closed-source%20models%20are%20tightly%20controlled%20by%20the%20companies%20that%20develop%20them.%20Chinese%20firms%20have%20largely%20favored%20the%20open-source%20route%2C%20while%20US%20tech%20giants%20have%20taken%20a%20more%20proprietary%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20US%20issued%20a%20warning%20against%20the%20use%20of%20US%20AI%20chips%20for%20Chinese%20models.%20It%20also%20issued%20new%20guidelines%20banning%20the%20use%20of%20Huawei's%20Ascend%20AI%20chips%20globally%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20chips%20were%20likely%20developed%20or%20produced%20in%20violation%20of%20US%20export%20controls%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20Commerce%20Department's%20Bureau%20of%20Industry%20and%20Security%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-says-us-china-very-close-ai-chip-race-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehardware%20divide%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20deepens%2C%20attention%20is%20also%20on%20software%20and%20AI%2C%20where%20control%20over%20the%20underlying%20mo